{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"22467eba1f","title":"致林彪、最荣臻电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dd64886cd4","index":0,"year":1935,"month":11,"day":19,"articleId":"22467eba1f"}],"tags":[{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji8","name":"毛泽东全集第8卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji8.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji8":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3978c43ed4","type":"paragraph","text":"致林彪、最荣臻电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"22467eba1f"},{"id":"229310b848","type":"paragraph","text":"（1935年11月19日）林、楚：（甲）董率一一一师（师长常恩多）本日如到张家湾，则明日有到黑水寺【之可能】，而在黑水寺、安家川之一个师明日有到直罗镇之可能。我军应准备后日（廿一）作战。明、后两日，你们应在安家川、直罗镇两点以北各设置一个观察哨。（乙）你们移驻位置即告。（丙）林看地形情况及对作战意见即告。（丁）我们已移到张村蜂西端之川口子，望派参课率武装一班来此接收命令。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"22467eba1f"},{"id":"4b5f5a7e6a","type":"paragraph","text":"彭毛十九日十九时","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"22467eba1f"}],"page":{"id":"eef6d35306","publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"22467eba1f","start":59,"end":59}}}},"__N_SSG":true}